# claude files

# ignore
configs/claude/**

# keep
!configs/claude/CLAUDE.md
!configs/claude/settings.json
!configs/claude/skills/
!configs/claude/skills/**
!configs/claude/statusline-command.sh

# Generated symlinks from link-dotfiles.sh for hostname-specific skills.
